      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">If the Unit Leader is within 2&quot;/5cm of a Unit Leader from a friendly Infantry Unit, then one Tank in this Unit may re-roll one failed To-Hit roll when targeting Infantry or Gun teams.</characteristic>
