      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Replace all M1 Garand rifle teams with Thompson SMG teams in any or all of your Rifle Platoons in this Formation for +2 points per Unit.RangeROF MOVEROF HALTAnti- tankFire- powerNOTES4&quot;/10cm3316Pinned ROF 1SKILLTRAINED4+SMG AssaultAssault3+SMG Assault: Platoons upgraded to Thompson SMG teams are rated Assault 3+.</characteristic>
