      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">This Formation may field an M7 Priest Artillery Battery (LU121) instead of a 105mm Cannon Platoon.WeaponRangeROF HaltROF MoveAnti- tankFire- powerNotesM7 Priest (105mm)72&quot;/ 180cmARTILLERY33+Forward Firing, Smoke Bombardmentor Direct Fire24&quot;/60cm1192+Brutal, Forward Firing, Slow Firing, SmokeM7 Priest (.50 cal MG)20&quot;/50cm3245+Self-defence AA</characteristic>
