      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Tank Riders: Infantry Teams from HQ and Rifle Platoons in this Formation can Shoot while Mounted on M4 Sherman Teams (to a maximum of one team per Tank), and can Dismount when Charging into Contact for +1 point per Unit.</characteristic>
