      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">When your Force is the Attacker, all 105mm Field Artillery Batteries (LU120) have a Firepower rating of 2+ (instead of the usual 3+) when they Repeat a Bombardment for +1 point per gun.</characteristic>
