      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">In this Formation, Rifle Platoons are -2 points each and other Units are -1 point each.  All Units lose Blood &apos;n Guts and have a Motivation rating as follows:MOTIVATIONRELUCTANT5+</characteristic>
