        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">When an Assault involving this Formation Commander is forced to Fall Back from Defensive Fire, immediately roll a Motivation Test. If successful, the Unit immediately Rallies from being Pinned Down and must immediately Charge into Contact a second time.</characteristic>
